@node "intro" "Inroduction"
@{b}@{u}Introduction@{ub}@{uu}
MouseCase is a bootutility that's easy to use. It allows you a selection from
several Startup-Sequences by an easy way.
Besides you can start programs who needs a special handling (e.g. Emulators,...).
Another advantage of using the mouse for selection is that no screen will be
opened. This is a big advantage for graphic-card users.
At this time you could select between 8 different startoptions
(including the normal Startup-Sequence).
@endnode

